OL,4,CUniversity new rules for bosses' pay
OL,5, University leaders have agreed to a new
OL,6, code on senior pay, which is expected
OL,7, to be published in the next few weeks.
OL,9,FUniversity representatives held a
OL,10,Fmeeting with minister Jo Johnson on
OL,11,FWednesday where they accepted the need
OL,12,Ffor more accountability.
OL,14,FIt follows fierce criticism of
OL,15,Funiversity leaders over claims of
OL,16,Fexcessive senior pay, with the head of
OL,17,Fthe University of Bath stepping down.
OL,19,FMr Johnson says "public confidence"
OL,20,Fover pay had to be restored.
